**Abstract:**
Essay dated May 31, 1993, written at Chantilly. Titled "Theology: From 'Historia' to 'Scientia'." Discusses 13th-century debate (1230-1265) over whether theology/Bible ("sacra pagina") could be transformed into Aristotelian science without loss. Proposes this shift represents early episode of the transformation analyzed by Hans Frei in *The Eclipse of Biblical Narrative*. Part of Chantilly book project.

